{"tid":758927,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《星球大戰9》公布卡士　已故嘉莉有份演！","createTime":"2018-07-28T06:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T17:56:53.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"250125fbc35b20868132ca914af31716abc87f82","tid":758927,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"《星球大戰9》（Star Wars Episode IX）近日正式公布卡士，演星戰要角「莉亞公主」的已故女星嘉莉菲莎（Carrie Fisher）落實有份「出演」！嘉莉於2016年因病離世，後來有指《星戰9》本身以她的角色為主，不過電影公司就講明不會以高科技令她「回歸」！導演JJ亞伯拉罕（J.J. Abrams）日前解畫，表示：「我哋永遠唔會重新搵演員代佢，又或者用CG角色。多得嘉莉囡囡Billie嘅支持同祝福，我哋搵到方法於《星戰9》紀念嘉莉嘅傳奇以及『莉亞公主』呢個角色，就係使用於《星戰7》未曝光嘅鏡頭。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一元老級要角「天行者」麥咸美（Mark Hamill），新鐵三角「Rey」黛絲烈尼（Daisy Ridley）、「Poe」Oscar Isaac以及「Finn」約翰保也加（John Boyega ）等都會現身《星戰9》。曾於正傳演「漢蘇奴」老友「蘭度」的Billy Dee Williams亦首度回歸星戰系列，Naomi Ackie與Richard E. Grant新加盟，角色細節暫時仍未公布。 <br />\n<br />\n《星戰9》導演由Colin Trevorrow換上2015年執導《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars：The Force Awakens，簡稱《星戰7》）的JJ亞伯拉罕掌鏡，他有份編劇，將要面對《星球大戰：最後絕地武士》（Star Wars：The Fast Jedi）的兩極影評，以及星戰外傳《韓索羅：星球大戰外傳》（Solo：A Star Wars Story）票房仆直的情況，未知能否拍出比《星戰7》更收得兼好評如潮的三部曲最終章？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180728/mobile/bkn-20180728103139753-0728_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180728%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180728103139753-0728_00862_001.html&d=Qs%2FWYXSXxEG7f5jIpYGn3mowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=e6fe9978\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180728/mobile/bkn-20180728103139753-0728_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c8941d9848ddb4babdb4d4923a30ddedf2e9cf3","tid":758927,"uid":1670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"Rian大導演表示拍電影完全唔需要考慮過左身嘅經典角色點樣埋尾，等ep9自然有人幫手執屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e84f9f0c81d33a8a481c51aa9f7db0b166a0078","tid":758927,"uid":87578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"《星戰9》導演由Colin Trevorrow換上2015年執導《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars：The Force Awakens，簡稱《星戰7》）的JJ亞伯拉罕掌鏡，他有份編劇，將要面對《星球大戰：最後絕地武士》<span style=\"color: red;\">（Star Wars：The Fast Jedi）</span>的兩極影評，以及星戰外傳《韓索羅：星球大戰外傳》（Solo：A Star Wars Story）票房仆直的情況，未知能否拍出比《星戰7》更收得兼好評如潮的三部曲最終章？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb23f5bd9de1393b527cb65811566ea2ae8bfee","tid":758927,"uid":17628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"其實搵邊個演唔係最大問題，問題係喺個劇本度"},{"pid":"300497938a61610becd5bbadb93e7b200c97c66f","tid":758927,"uid":174654,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"rose都有份演...又要睇佢同finn啲感情線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/151046_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F151046_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=29c3595a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34961e994db71f9cad081fcec670f07447a58f14","tid":758927,"uid":58413,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"300497938a61610becd5bbadb93e7b200c97c66f","tid":758927,"uid":174654,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"rose都有份演...又要睇佢同finn啲感情線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/151046_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F151046_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=29c3595a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply